events.text: I was so stupid to sign in to this many projects!
It's just not possible to do everything, even if I give up on sleep.
It's serious, haven't done anything important for days, maybe months.
Only few tiny spikes of energy, evenings of hyperfocus that makes other people thinks I'm OK. I really want somebody to notice I'm not.
I was thinking how wonderful it would be in mental hospital, where my only responsibility would be to figure myself out and heal.
Even if I would sneak to this Adrianne rocket and go to the Moon.
Sneak into the rocket nad become a Moon Princess, I have nothing to lose anyway.
